"  <dt><notr>Taʻuluaalofi</notr></dt><dd>(\"Taʻulua Westward\") Sirius seen "
"at sunset.</dd>\n"
"  <dt><notr>Aolele</notr></dt><dd>(\"Flying Cloud\") Small Magellanic Cloud."
